        "meta_description": "In a new interview, 'Mrs. Doubtfire' actress Lisa Jakub recalled Robin Williams advocating for her after her school kicked her out while she was filming the movie. Williams wrote a letter asking them to reconsider, but was ultimately unsuccessful.",
        "meta_lang": "en",
